Benchmark / dry-run fixture
===========================

A minimal directory tree used for two purposes:

1. Correctness check — run `asimov --dry-run tests/fixture` and verify the
   output matches the expected set below.

2. Reproducible benchmark — `make bench` times both v0.5.x and v0.4.2 against
   this tree so results are comparable across machines and runs.

Expected to be EXCLUDED (sentinel present beside dep dir)
----------------------------------------------------------
  node-project/node_modules          (sentinel: package.json)
  rust-project/target                (sentinel: Cargo.toml)
  python-requirements/.venv          (sentinel: requirements.txt)
  python-pyproject/.venv             (sentinel: pyproject.toml)
  ruby-project/vendor                (sentinel: Gemfile)
  php-project/vendor                 (sentinel: composer.json)
  go-project/vendor                  (sentinel: go.mod)
  elixir-project/deps                (sentinel: mix.exs)
  elixir-project/_build              (sentinel: mix.exs)
  swift-project/.build               (sentinel: Package.swift)
  monorepo/frontend/node_modules     (sentinel: package.json)
  monorepo/backend/target            (sentinel: Cargo.toml)
  monorepo/shared/vendor             (sentinel: go.mod)

Expected to be SKIPPED (no sentinel)
-------------------------------------
  no-sentinel/node_modules           (no package.json present)
